# galaxy-evolution Quality Roadmap

**Author:** Kun
**Date:** 2026-05-12 21:00 KST
**Goal:** push galaxy-evolution from q=0.894 → q≥0.95+ via the autowiki_tick loop
**Audience:** Tori (implementer), HwaO (coordinator), Papa
**Companion docs:** `autowiki_loop_v1.md` (pipeline spec), `arxiv_wiki_feed_design_v1.md` (ingest)

This doc is grounded in a live audit of `autowiki_runs` on Mac Studio (2026-05-12 ~12:00 UTC). Numbers are reproducible — every section has its supporting SQL or code reference.

