## TF-IDF Classifier Content Window Bug (2026-05-12)

`_page_text()` in `arxiv_classifier.py` caps content at 1,500 chars from a 33k-char page.
Even directly relevant papers score below 0.30 threshold (galaxy-evolution max cosine 0.19).
Fix: raise content cap to 5,000 chars or add per-page keyword override.
Effort: ~0.5d Tori.
